text: Zawedde "Zawe" Ashton (; born 25 July 1984) is an English actress, playwright and director. She is best known for her roles in Channel 4 comedy dramas Not Safe for Work and Fresh Meat. She also starred in Blitz, St Trinian's 2: The Legend of Fritton's Gold and Velvet Buzzsaw. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English child actors Category:English television actors Category:English stage actors Category:English radio actors Category:English voice actors Category:English playwrights Category:English television directors Category:Actors from London Category:Writers from London
